data.description: Open concept split plan 3 Bed 2 Bath home. Large Kitchen, Soaring ceilings throughout. Gorgeous granite in kitchen and baths. The walk in closets with built in shelving provide plenty of storage. Step in pantry, new carpet, fresh interior paint, covered back porch with an additional patio. Turn key ready. Pride in ownership is present throughout. The kitchen, living room and dining room flow into a comfortable feel that is great for entertaining and family time. The large granite island accents the open comfortable kitchen living room transition. Ample soft close cabinets and drawers . Play or relax in the privacy fenced back yard. Walk or bike to the nearby private park with picnic areas, extensive modern playground and walking track. The location provides for easy access in and out as well as to Sam Houston State University, Shopping, The Woodlands area, schools,  medical facilities and much more. This is a must see at this condition, location and price. 3 miles from town.
